# Apply Leave Functionality of HRM Site
This specification verifies the Apply Leave functionality of Leave Module

## Apply Leave
* Open Chrome Browser
* Goto the login page of HRM Demo URL "https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/"
* Enter username "Admin" and password "admin123"
* Click on Login button
* Click on Leave Module Tab
* Click on Apply Leave 
* Select Leave Type as "US - Personal"
* Enter From Date "2020-10-26" and To Date "2020-10-26"
* Provide the comments
* Click on Apply
* Click on Logout Button
* Close Chrome Browser